<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann von Wittelsbach, Herzog von Pfalz-Neumarkt</head><p>Der kündigt Niklas Grieß, Diener der Stadt, wegen Friedrich von Egloffstein an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_159" id="79v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_159_r1l3">Hercʒog <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_159_r1l4">Gnedıger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als vvir nehſt ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> erber botſchaft cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_159_r1l5">geſant heten als von Fricʒen von Eglofſteins vvegen etc / Alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_159_r1l7">ſenden vvir yecʒunden 
<add><ab facs="#facs_159_r1l6">darümb </ab></add> cʒu <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden Nẏclas Grieſʒen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_159_r1l9"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener 
<add><ab facs="#facs_159_r1l8">dauon cʒureden </ab></add> / Vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / vvaʒ derſelbe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> diener in <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_159_r1l10">ſache cʒu diſem mal etc vt in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die <expan>walp<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_159" id="79v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir nehst
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> erber botschaft czu
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> gesant heten als von Friczen von Eglofsteins
                        wegen etc., also senden wir yeczunden <add>darümb</add> czu
                                <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden Nyclas Grieszen,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, <add>davon czu reden</add>. Und
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, waz derselbe
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener in
                            <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache czu disem mal etc. ut in
                                <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                                <expan>Walp<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>en.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
